{"tid":2214276,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"辯方邀專家實驗：女子難掟10米","createTime":"2020-09-23T06:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T08:14:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8e1f7037b7c466c724cb302bf9afcedbabbd5cd0","tid":2214276,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T06:42:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200923/4GA3CGBXPZCENK53XD3LS2TGTQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200923%2F4GA3CGBXPZCENK53XD3LS2TGTQ%2F&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9iWHaP8IcnP89ZPrefCyuoo%3D&h=46096d09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200923%2F4GA3CGBXPZCENK53XD3LS2TGTQ%2F&h=4afd4dbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200923/4GA3CGBXPZCENK53XD3LS2TGTQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n辯方邀專家實驗：女子難掟10米<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/77ePGZMBZrpWT0mV4gbG-hIqQlo=/2248x1319/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4CEODYVIMFETRK65LQMJUG4MXE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F77ePGZMBZrpWT0mV4gbG-hIqQlo%3D%2F2248x1319%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4CEODYVIMFETRK65LQMJUG4MXE.jpg&h=ed39ff61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警員徐德華指遭被告在十米外掟磚，盤問下改稱兩人相距約八米。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】被告鄭卓敏被裁定表證成立後選擇不自辯，但呈上良好品格信件及傳召認識逾20年的同窗擔任證人，透露被告是右撇子，反駁指控她用左手掟磚的證供。被告並邀請中文大學教授就掟磚距離撰寫專家報告，找來16名身高、體重相若的女子進行掟磚測試，經過256次投擲，平均距離為約5至7米，當中只得一人在其中一次測試中成功擲到10米距離。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：認誇大證供指控女子飛磚襲擊  警庭上狂改口供 磚細一半 距縮兩米<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n體形相若16人測試<br />\n<br />\n據警員徐德華（譯音）錄取的口供，被告當日向他掟一塊長20厘米、闊10厘米的磚頭，兩人相距10米，磚頭最終落在徐腳前。辯方為此邀請中大教授進行研究，若一名普通女子投擲一塊尺寸為長20厘米、闊10厘米、高5厘米，重約2.6公斤的磚頭，可以投擲多遠。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，研究共邀請16名女子參加測試，年齡介乎22至33歲，身高約1.6米，體重則介乎51至65公斤。每名參加者均需以四種不同的姿勢、分別以左手及右手投擲上述磚頭兩次，平均距離為5至7米，其中右手所擲結果較佳。控方沒對報告提出質疑。<br />\n<br />\n與被告同在加拿大留學的辯方證人Elly Mau形容，。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"4e32c2f9fed4342e7f719db3f21dd048c7d6c319","tid":2214276,"uid":327010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T08:13:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ab890d32cc0f4e19ec2b6192345668dd10df589","tid":2214276,"uid":327010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T08:13:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03789f3bca248fcd4ca02713025be60ee7e54004","tid":2214276,"uid":327010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T08:14:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}